---

<Layout
  title="Navam Invest - AI-Powered Investment Intelligence for Retail Investors"
  description="Professional-grade investment analysis with 10 specialized AI agents. Runs on your laptop for $3-15/month. Open source, privacy-first, battle-tested. 95% cheaper than traditional wealth management."
  keywords="AI investment tool, investment intelligence, portfolio management, AI stock analysis, tax-loss harvesting, options strategies, retail investor tools, AI agents"
  ogImage="/refer/images/navam-invest/starting.png"
  ogType="product"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(productSchema)} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(howToSchema)} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />

  <Header client:load />

  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 via-purple-900 to-pink-900 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20"></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
            Professional Investment Intelligence
            <span class="block mt-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-200 to-pink-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
              On Your Laptop
            </span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 text-white/90">
            10 specialized AI agents provide professional-grade investment analysis for <strong>$3-15/month</strong>.
            That's 95% cheaper than traditional wealth management.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <Button client:load variant="primary" size="lg" href="https://github.com/navam-io/navam-invest">
              View on GitHub
            </Button>
            <Button client:load variant="secondary" size="lg" href="#installation">
              Get Started
            </Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Features -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-center mb-16">10 Specialized AI Agents</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üéØ Quill - Equity Analyst</h3>
            <p>Comprehensive fundamental analysis, DCF valuation, comparable company analysis, and detailed investment theses.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üìä Earnings Whisperer</h3>
            <p>Track earnings surprises, analyze earnings call transcripts, identify post-earnings drift opportunities.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üîç Screen Forge</h3>
            <p>Systematically screen thousands of stocks based on quality, momentum, value, and thematic factors.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üåç Macro Lens</h3>
            <p>Top-down macroeconomic analysis and sector allocation guidance for current market regimes.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üì∞ News Sentry</h3>
            <p>Monitor real-time market events, SEC filings, analyst actions, and trading anomalies.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üõ°Ô∏è Risk Shield</h3>
            <p>Portfolio exposure analysis, value-at-risk calculations, scenario testing, and drawdown monitoring.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üí∞ Tax Scout</h3>
            <p>Identify tax-loss harvesting opportunities, check wash-sale violations, optimize rebalancing strategies.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üé≠ Hedge Smith</h3>
            <p>Design options strategies for portfolio protection and yield enhancement (collars, covered calls).</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">üìà Factor Scout</h3>
            <p>Analyze factor exposures, measure style tilts, assess portfolio alignment with market regimes.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">‚öñÔ∏è Rebalance Bot</h3>
            <p>Detect portfolio drift, optimize rebalancing, minimize taxes during portfolio adjustments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Installation Section -->
    <section id="installation" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-center mb-12">Installation</h2>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Get started in under 2 minutes:</h3>

            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">1. Install Python 3.9+</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Ensure Python 3.9 or higher is installed on your system.</p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">2. Install Navam Invest</h4>
                <div class="bg-gray-900 text-green-400 p-4 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm">
                  pip install navam-invest
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">3. Configure API Keys</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Create a <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded">.env</code> file with your Anthropic API key:</p>
                <div class="bg-gray-900 text-green-400 p-4 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm">
                  ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key_here
                </div>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">4. Launch</h4>
                <div class="bg-gray-900 text-green-400 p-4 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm">
                  navam invest
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">üí° Optional Enhancements</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Add free-tier API keys for enhanced data:</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600">
                <li>Financial Modeling Prep (company financials)</li>
                <li>Alpha Vantage (market data)</li>
                <li>Polygon.io (real-time quotes)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-center mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="border-b pb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">What is Navam Invest?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Navam Invest is an AI-powered investment intelligence tool that runs entirely on your laptop. It combines 10 specialized AI agents to provide professional-grade investment analysis for typically $3-15 per month in API usage costs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-b pb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">How much does it cost?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Navam Invest is free and open source (MIT License). You only pay for the API costs of Claude AI, which typically range from $3-15 per month depending on usage. This is 95%+ cheaper than traditional wealth management services that charge $1,000-$10,000 per year.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-b pb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Is my financial data secure?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Yes. Navam Invest runs entirely on your laptop using your own API keys. Your portfolio information, queries, and analyses never leave your device except for API calls to Claude (which you control). This is a privacy-first, local-execution design.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-b pb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">What operating systems are supported?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Navam Invest runs on Windows, macOS, and Linux. It requires Python 3.9 or higher and works in any terminal environment.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-b pb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Do I need to be a developer to use it?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">No. Installation is simple (pip install navam-invest), and the interface uses natural language. Just ask questions in plain English like "What are the risks in my portfolio?" or "Should I buy Apple stock?"</p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">What are the 10 AI agents?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700">The 10 specialized agents are: Quill (equity analyst), Earnings Whisperer (earnings analysis), Screen Forge (stock screening), Macro Lens (macroeconomic analysis), News Sentry (news monitoring), Risk Shield (risk management), Tax Scout (tax optimization), Hedge Smith (options strategies), Factor Scout (factor analysis), and Rebalance Bot (portfolio rebalancing).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900 to-blue-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join retail investors who are getting professional-grade investment intelligence without the professional price tag.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <Button client:load variant="primary" size="lg" href="https://github.com/navam-io/navam-invest">
            View on GitHub
          </Button>
          <Button client:load variant="secondary" size="lg" href="/blog/introducing-navam-invest">
            Read the Blog Post
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer client:load />
</Layout>
